author: Reuters
title: Shandong New Beiyang Information Technology lowers amount for private placement
text:
Oct 15 Shandong New Beiyang Information Technology Co Ltd
* Says adjusts share private placement, to raise up to 860 million yuan ($135.54 million) from 1.5 billion yuan previously
Source text in Chinese: bit.ly/1MDaJKk ; bit.ly/1LO7LO1
 ($1 = 6.3450 Chinese yuan renminbi) (Reporting by Hong Kong and Singapore newsrooms)
